    </ObjectDataProvider>&#xD;The two identical Base64 encoded strings decode to a GZIP-compressed Windows executable. Virustotal doesn't see anything wrong with them [2]. Hyprid Analysis labels it as malicious [3]. The string "Project Discovery CVE-2025-5086" may point to the scan originating from a vulnerability scanner.
